title: 'Yellowstone' Episodes 4-5 Recap
description:
Chris Ryan and Ryen Russillo saddle up to talk about the latest in the Paramount+ drama, including the show's perfect line delivery, breaking down Summer Higgins, and the three gods of Texas.
Hosts: Chris Ryan and Ryen Russillo
Producer: Steve Ahlman
